column5: Hi and Happy New Year:  Just wondering when the Fishing for Tyler event is?? I am donating my original Racoons painting.  Pam
Wow thats very generous of you Pam !  Happy New Year ... hopefully I'll be able to  there this year too... last year it conflicted with Lake Trout openers on Lake Joe ..
From what Maureen told me it is Saturday Febuary 23 at Innisfil Beach Park.   vance
Very nice Pam, thank you!!!!  Vance is correct it is on Sat. Feb. 23  Are you going to make the trip this year or do you need my address again  Maureen
I'll be mailing it along...maybe ONE of these years I'll make it there.  If your address is the same as last year, I have it on file.  Thanks Maureen.  Pam
